data.description: turnkey - bring your pickiest buyer! there's so much to love about this lovingly upgraded home, brimming with character and charm. Open and inviting kitchen and breakfast nook, perfect space for a coffee bar. this charming home boasts a large cozy den area with a working wood burning stove and a custom hearth made from reclaimed handmade brick from the historic American Cigar Co. built in 1903. It makes for the absolute best snuggly movie nights or picture perfect Christmas mornings. huge bow window where your favorite house plants will thrive and fill the room with beautiful light. custom built floating vanity/desk in third bedroom. laundry room with plenty of room and shelving for storage. neighborhood is quiet and tucked away in what feels out of the way of the city but is near schools, restaurants and shopping centers, making it ideally located. don't miss out on this special home!
